high_descs: turn around and walk to the end of the room, then hang a right and walk to the end of the room again, turn right to face the kitchen counter
grab the spatula off of the counter
move to the end of the room ahead, then take a left and move to the sink at the end of the room
place the spatula inside of the sink and clean it off, then pick it back up
back up a bit and face the kitchen stove on your right
place the spatula inside of the pull out drawer to the right of the stove
anns.task_desc: place a clean spatula inside of the pull out drawer

high_descs: Turn right, and then right again and walk to the door. Turn right  walk towards the white table. Face the table.
Pick up the metal spatula on the table.
Walk towards the door again, then turn left and walk towards the sink
Place the spatula in the sink and turn on the faucet so water fills the sink. Turn off water.
Take out the spatula, then turn right to face the oven and the stove top. Open the top drawer to the right of the stove
Place the spatula in the drawer then close it.
anns.task_desc: Find the spatula on the table, clean it, then place it in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room head to the table
Pick up the turner on the table beside the plate
Turn to your right, walk a few steps then turn to your left and head to the sink
Put the turner on the sink, rinse it
Pick up the turner then turn around walk towards the toaster
Open the cabinet below the toaster and put the turner inside beside the knife, then close it
anns.task_desc: Place the clean turner in the cabinet
